name: NSAIDOTCMigraineAttackMedication
title: NSAID OTC Migraine Attack Medication
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent concepts for over the counter (OTC) non-steroidal anti-inflammatory drugs (NSAIDs) for migraine attacks.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element in the QDM category of medication.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts that describe NSAID over the counter medications.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts that describe over the counter cold and flu medications that may contain pain relievers.)
